Broadcast Service
________________________________________________________________________________

Broadcast Service is the central hub which broadcasts messages to the recipients
over a websocket connection. The purpose of isolating the message broadcast from
the message faucet is to allow for a more scalable broadcast to many client
connections from multiple instances.

This service is just one of many pieces for a yet-to-be-named toy project of
mine to create a from-scratch native chatting application.

